import { Container, Grid, Typography, Card, CardMedia, CardContent, CardActions, Button } from '@material-ui/core'
import ThumbUpIcon from '@material-ui/icons/ThumbUp';
import { makeStyles } from '@material-ui/core'
import './posts.css'

const useStyles = makeStyles({
    container : {
        marginTop : 100,
        background : "yellow"
    }
})
const Posts = () =>{

    const classes = useStyles()

    return(
        <Container className={classes.container}>
            <Grid container>
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} xl={3} spacing={4}>
                    <Card>
                        <CardMedia 
                            component="img"
                            alt=''
                            title=''
                            height="200"
                            image=''
                        />
                        <CardContent>
                            <Typography variant="h4">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.</Typography>

                            <Typography variant="body2" component="p">Lorem ipsum dolor sit 
                                amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Reiciendis nostrum 
                                impedit deleniti optio asperiores necessitatibus error iusto 
                                minus! Earum, molestias!
                            </Typography>
                        </CardContent>
                        <CardActions>
                            <Button startIcon={<ThumbUpIcon/>}></Button>
                            <Typography variant="p">20 Likes</Typography>
                            <Button>See more</Button>
                        </CardActions>
                    </Card>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Posts
